ill not compile against 2.0.0-M1 because those classes are absent from the resolved artifact.\",\n    \"Do not add pekko-actor-typed_2.13 unless the workflow intentionally wants to test the separate typed actor module; it is not required to cover pekko-actor_2.13 itself.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e8f6e6aecd80a64016a403e4e3ba48193976c376f9934a0b0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 14768, "output": 726, "cacheRead": 20480, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35974, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782595137781, "responseId": "resp_0e8f6e6aecd80a64016a403e42bee0819385e1a42437c4880c"}}
